ok, heres what ill say, a thing your going to need to look at is "the meta" of champions that are good, great, ect.
not saying you need to play them you can get anywhere with anyone but meta will be easier, but you will need to learn how to fight champions based off who you want to main, look up counter for your champ(s) so you know who to essentially ban and learn to roam, farm well ect. cant explain too much out of a discord/skype call but thats all up to you, im not the best im gold 5 but figured i could help :P
